  "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds the complete **V12 Scale & Operating Cadence** layer on top of V1–V11\n- Converts the First Revenue Sprint into a repeatable weekly operating system\n- Introduces data-driven scale decisions across sales capacity, service margin, client health, and automation\n\n## What's included\n\n| المكوّن | الملفات |\n|---|---|\n| Scale Master Plan | `scale/SCALE_MASTER_PLAN_AR.md` |\n| Weekly Operating Rhythm | `cadence/WEEKLY_OPERATING_RHYTHM_AR.md` |\n| Monthly Scale Review | `cadence/MONTHLY_SCALE_REVIEW_AR.md` |\n| Client Portfolio Review | `portfolio/CLIENT_PORTFOLIO_REVIEW_AR.md` |\n| Sales Capacity & Quotas | `scale/SALES_CAPACITY_AND_QUOTAS_AR.md` |\n| Service Margin System | `scale/SERVICE_MARGIN_SYSTEM_AR.md` |\n| Hiring & Delegation Cadence | `scale/HIRING_AND_DELEGATION_CADENCE_AR.md` |\n| Automation Backlog System | `automation-backlog/AUTOMATION_BACKLOG_SYSTEM_AR.md` |\n| Partner Quota & Scorecard | `partners/PARTNER_QUOTA_AND_SCORECARD_AR.md` |\n| Scale Observability Plan | `observability/SCALE_OBSERVABILITY_PLAN_AR.md` |\n| Scale Operating Scorecard | `ops/SCALE_OPERATING_SCORECARD_AR.md` |\n| V12 QA Checklist | `qa/V12_SCALE_QA_CHECKLIST_AR.md` |\n| GitHub Actions Workflow | `.github/workflows/dealix-v12-scale-cadence.yml` |\n| Frontend: Scale Ops page | `frontend/src/app/[locale]/scale-ops/page.tsx` |\n| Frontend: Scale Control Tower | `frontend/src/app/[locale]/internal/scale-control/page.tsx` |\n| 9 Python operational scripts | `scripts/dealix_v12_*.py`, `scripts/dealix_*_*.py` |\n\n## Key rules enforced in V12\n\n- No automated external sends — all outputs require human review before sending\n- No scaling unproven channels — expand only what's already working\n- No automation before 3 manual successes\n- No hiring before a clear bottleneck is identified\n- Pilot pricing (499 SAR) only viable if scope stays tight or converts to retainer fast\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Run `python scripts/dealix_v12_readiness_check.py` → expect 